{"tid":2036651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最好or最壞嘅打算  Plan C!!!!!","createTime":"2020-05-26T14:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T04:05:37.000Z","uid":119585,"like":31,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8427366f68447cf70e605cdf7efc1c4e8f0d066d","tid":2036651,"uid":119585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:56:04.000Z","msg":"暫時plan A同plan B 分別係黎明行動同圍堵立法會，不過如大家所見，都極具質疑，始終好難阻止到惡歌法以及國安法係立法會到通過，擔心最終犧牲嘅只有手足。<br />\n<br />\n呢個post唔係要大家放棄呢兩個plan，而係希望當呢兩個plan都失敗嘅話，亦都係惡歌法係成功通過嘅話，我地軍心一定會重創。所以Plan C嘅目的係繼續凝聚我哋，話比全世界知，我地唔會就咁氣餒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對於國際戰線方面，都可以打得好好睇睇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要返工嘅 聽日唔打算出去嘅 我知你地唔會甘心淨係留喺屋企 <br />\n<br />\n27／5  夜晚8:00  <br />\n全港18區      每區都搞一個集會（借搞武漢肺炎講座）<br />\n行動方面： 嗌口號 唱國歌等 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（請自由發揮） </span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後 如果可行嘅話我希望區議員or公眾人士 可以幫幫手搞呢個武漢肺炎講座<br />\n<br />\n正皮：ok喎<br />\n負皮：不了"},{"pid":"0aba5ec815d6ba5c23f5a50f605572c521615470","tid":2036651,"uid":119585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:56:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c548e2b83e22846da3cbce1b0c6476f67e9bfb08","tid":2036651,"uid":119585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:56:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e7af155d91d1e978e4c8c291cfba2cf85f78e23d","tid":2036651,"uid":354682,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:57:15.000Z","msg":"why not all<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c302aa2da79c0dc043e5b0d22e6984420962ee53","tid":2036651,"uid":119585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:58:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2d6f5ff919970df54318541fc4452c20c214522f","tid":2036651,"uid":119585,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e7af155d91d1e978e4c8c291cfba2cf85f78e23d","t